Ne.

01:16:40.052 --> 01:16:41.953
Otpušten si.

01:16:42.055 --> 01:16:43.354
Otpušten?

01:16:44.657 --> 01:16:47.058
Imaš problema sa sluhom?

01:16:48.394 --> 01:16:51.229
