01:17:09.249 --> 01:17:12.641
Jebote, jebote,

01:17:14.687 --> 01:17:16.086
Ne, šefe.

01:17:16.689 --> 01:17:19.524
Ako samo budem sanjao
da si me ocinkao,

01:17:19.526 --> 01:17:22.060
otkinut ću ti jebenu
glavu s ovom golf palicom.

01:17:22.062 --> 01:17:23.461
Čuješ li me?

01:17:23.463 --> 01:17:28.847
Je li jasno? - Da!
